to read it anyway,

777
00:48:39,120 --> 00:48:41,280
and when I ask you
what your plan is,

778
00:48:41,360 --> 00:48:42,320
you say...

779
00:48:42,360 --> 00:48:47,800
"I don't know."

780
00:48:47,880 --> 00:48:49,440
Do you think I'm lying?

781
00:48:49,520 --> 00:48:50,520
I've had a very
difficult few weeks.

782
00:48:50,600 --> 00:48:52,800
Which, of course,
you did not write about.

783
00:48:52,880 --> 00:48:56,880
Mr. Giamoro, tell me honestly.

784
00:48:56,920 --> 00:48:58,480
Why don't you drop out?

785
00:48:58,520 --> 00:49:00,040
I mean, why are you here?

786
00:49:00,120 --> 00:49:01,880
To taunt me?

787
00:49:02,840 --> 00:49:03,880
It's not my way to drop out.

788
00:49:03,960 --> 00:49:04,880
Yes, yes, yes.

789
00:49:04,960 --> 00:49:08,320
But why are you here in this class?

790
00:49:11,080 --> 00:49:12,560
I don't know.

791
00:49:14,520 --> 00:49:17,000
