nerve here, Jackie?

801
00:49:39,160 --> 00:49:41,800
Fill those pages!
Go out!

802
00:49:41,880 --> 00:49:45,400
Get a new Journal and fill the pages!

803
00:49:45,480 --> 00:49:51,040
Write about it.

804
00:49:52,320 --> 00:49:53,280
Yes?

805
00:49:54,880 --> 00:49:55,920
Okay.

806
00:49:57,760 --> 00:49:58,720
Thank you.

807
00:50:03,880 --> 00:50:07,360
I miss that time in my life,
when I was fearless,

808
00:50:07,440 --> 00:50:09,720
when the ground
was mine and I stood it,

809
00:50:09,760 --> 00:50:12,960
when I was bullheaded like my dad,
and I was always right.

810
00:50:14,600 --> 00:50:16,680
Mr. Giamoro,
I have told you before

811
00:50:16,760 --> 00:50:18,520
that you cannot
make these outbursts.

812
00:50:18,560 --> 00:50:23,280
