That's fine.

814
00:50:25,000 --> 00:50:27,400
But Just hear me out,
because this is important to understand.

815
00:50:27,480 --> 00:50:29,800
We built this company, okay?

816
00:50:29,880 --> 00:50:31,200
We put our souls into it.

817
00:50:31,280 --> 00:50:32,960
We made it what it is!

818
00:50:33,000 --> 00:50:35,080
And now that it's worth something,
ten years later,

819
00:50:35,160 --> 00:50:37,280
our former employers
want to rip it to shit!

820
00:50:37,320 --> 00:50:39,520
Okay, I'm sorry.
Bailiff!

821
00:50:39,560 --> 00:50:41,280
You Just bought yourself
a night in Jail.

822
00:50:41,360 --> 00:50:42,720
Wait a minute!
Hold on a second!

823
00:50:42,800 --> 00:50:45,440
Ten years is too late
to come along

824
00:50:45,480 --> 00:50:48,520
