110 people into the gutter!

825
00:50:48,600 --> 00:50:50,360
It's not right, goddamn it!

826
00:50:50,440 --> 00:50:53,520
Get off me!
I can walk out on my own!

827
00:50:53,640 --> 00:50:55,400
I can walk out on my own!

828
00:50:57,200 --> 00:51:01,960
I was always ready to explode
if I thought you needed to learn a lesson,

829
00:51:02,000 --> 00:51:06,280
if I thought you were in the way of me,
the way I needed things to be.

830
00:51:14,400 --> 00:51:15,320
You're a fool.

831
00:51:15,400 --> 00:51:17,280
Yes, I know that.

832
00:51:17,320 --> 00:51:18,880
But damn, were you cute.

833
00:51:18,920 --> 00:51:20,520
Wow. I mean...

834
00:51:20,600 --> 00:51:23,320
That all changed for me, though.

835
00:51:23,400 --> 00:51:26,840
It changed a little bit
every time Nina kissed me.

836
00:51:26,920 --> 00:51:30,080
Jack, the Jury went our way.

837
00:51:30,160 --> 00:51:31,360
What?

838
00:51:31,400 --> 00:51:33,120
We won, Jack.

839
00:51:33,200 --> 00:51:35,160
- We won?
- We won.

840
00:51:38,520 --> 00:51:40,480
Oh, my God!

841
00:51:48,720 --> 00:51:50,560
The winning streak continued.

842
00:51:50,600 --> 00:51:52,360
The agency grew.

843
00:52:00,680 --> 00:52:02,440
Things got sweet.

844
00:52:02,520 --> 00:52:07,200
The little moments took light
and the darkness lost ground.

845
00:52:08,360 --> 00:52:12,800
Promises were made
and dreams were laid out.

846
00:52:12,880 --> 00:52:17,600
