866
00:53:08,880 --> 00:53:11,120
Rickshaw Inn,
downtown on Broadway.

867
00:53:11,200 --> 00:53:12,160
Do you know it?

868
00:53:12,240 --> 00:53:13,160
Chinatown. Yeah.

869
00:53:13,240 --> 00:53:15,120
My family used to eat there
on Sundays when I was a boy.

870
00:53:15,160 --> 00:53:18,800
I'll see you there
for dinner tomorrow night, 6:00.

871
00:53:26,520 --> 00:53:28,240
Get out! Get out!

872
00:53:28,320 --> 00:53:29,760
