879
00:55:30,200 --> 00:55:31,800
Bunch of rich white men.

880
00:55:31,880 --> 00:55:32,840
Rich white gatekeepers.

881
00:55:32,920 --> 00:55:34,680
What?

882
00:55:37,280 --> 00:55:39,520
Is that the line she gave you

883
00:55:39,600 --> 00:55:43,480
