884
00:55:43,560 --> 00:55:46,800
Let me tell you something, Jimmy.

885
00:55:46,880 --> 00:55:50,360
You've got nothing out there
protecting you.

886
00:55:50,400 --> 00:55:51,800
There's nothing.

887
00:55:52,640 --> 00:55:54,320
No security. No gate.

888
00:55:54,400 --> 00:55:56,800
No hidden camera.
No patrols.

889
00:55:56,880 --> 00:55:58,400
Anybody can Just walk in off the street

890
00:55:58,480 --> 00:56:00,880
and put a cap in
the back of your head.

891
00:56:00,960 --> 00:56:02,040
Now where's my Journal?

892
00:56:02,080 --> 00:56:03,440
And don't say, "Fuck you,"

893
00:56:03,520 --> 00:56:05,360
