it was a robbery gone bad.

896
00:56:10,720 --> 00:56:12,760
Where is my Journal?

897
00:56:12,840 --> 00:56:15,920
All you had to do
was answer my calls,

898
00:56:16,000 --> 00:56:17,360
read her scripts.

899
00:56:17,440 --> 00:56:18,840
But no, you couldn't do that.

900
00:56:18,920 --> 00:56:20,120
You're too big time, huh?

901
00:56:20,960 --> 00:56:22,840
You're never gonna
see that Journal again.

902
00:56:41,440 --> 00:56:43,600
Hi. I need to see
Dr. Sands right away.

903
00:56:43,680 --> 00:56:46,080
He's with a patient, sir.

904
00:56:46,160 --> 00:56:47,800
Okay, that doesn't
work for me, so...

905
00:56:47,880 --> 00:56:51,040
- Maybe you should have a seat or...
- It's fine. Don't worry about it.

906
00:56:51,080 --> 00:56:52,080
Dr. Sands!

907
00:56:56,160 --> 00:56:57,200
Excuse me, sir.
I'm sorry.

908
00:56:57,280 --> 00:56:59,520
