your appointment to a later date.

909
00:56:59,560 --> 00:57:02,040
Would you mind stepping out
to the waiting room?

910
00:57:02,120 --> 00:57:04,040
The receptionist will
take care of you.

911
00:57:04,120 --> 00:57:06,600
Sir, we're done with you.

912
00:57:07,360 --> 00:57:08,800
Do these look
like teeth to you?

913
00:57:08,880 --> 00:57:10,520
I can fix them.
You wouldn't sit still.

914
00:57:10,560 --> 00:57:11,840
I couldn't get the mold right.
