00:57:13,280 --> 00:57:15,440
Cancel his appointments
for the rest of the day.

917
00:57:17,000 --> 00:57:19,520
Get fixing, Skippy.

918
00:57:24,160 --> 00:57:26,200
No one knows what
we're talking about, okay?

919
00:57:26,280 --> 00:57:27,200
Try to act professional.

920
00:57:27,280 --> 00:57:28,240
I'll try.

921
00:57:28,320 --> 00:57:29,440
Hey, Arlene!

922
00:57:30,240 --> 00:57:32,160
