924
00:57:34,240 --> 00:57:36,480
I'm having dinner there
tonight at 6:00.

925
00:57:36,520 --> 00:57:38,240
After that, I've got
a little something planned.

926
00:57:38,320 --> 00:57:39,920
And after that,

927
00:57:40,000 --> 00:57:41,920
