931
00:58:00,960 --> 00:58:02,160
Maybe he's having dinner here with Phil.

932
00:58:02,240 --> 00:58:03,760
Maybe they patched it up.

933
00:58:04,160 --> 00:58:05,360
Maybe he's here
to sign the tooth fairy.

934
00:58:05,400 --> 00:58:06,880
You got a better shot at that.

935
00:58:07,520 --> 00:58:09,160
I'd take ten percent
of the tooth fairy.

936
00:58:09,240 --> 00:58:10,640
Who owns the tooth fairy?

937
00:58:10,680 --> 00:58:11,680
Yeah. Is it public domain?

938
00:58:11,760 --> 00:58:13,440
That's not a bad idea.
Find out.

939
00:58:18,840 --> 00:58:20,400
He's here. He's here.
He's here.

940
00:58:25,720 --> 00:58:29,040
Mr. Giamoro.
How are you doing?

941
00:58:29,120 --> 00:58:31,600
The Asian girl from Primkin's class.

942
00:58:31,680 --> 00:58:33,840
Yep. The Asian girl.

943
00:58:33,920 --> 00:58:36,200
So, what came first,
the class or the story?

944
00:58:36,280 --> 00:58:37,840
The story.

945
00:58:37,920 --> 00:58:39,400
Who's that girl?

946
00:58:39,480 --> 00:58:40,440
I have no idea.

947
00:58:42,480 --> 00:58:45,720
