a guy like you?

951
00:58:53,680 --> 00:58:55,160
Well, to be honest with you, Barbi,

952
00:58:55,240 --> 00:58:58,960
I think I took that class
for two reasons.

953
00:58:59,000 --> 00:59:01,440
One, I wanted to
expand my horizons.

954
00:59:01,520 --> 00:59:05,000
And two...
and there's some irony in this...

955
00:59:05,080 --> 00:59:06,520
