gonna take place.

1005
01:02:43,560 --> 01:02:46,640
Either I'm gonna represent you
or I'm going to Jail.

1006
01:02:46,720 --> 01:02:48,520
So, hear me out.

1007
01:02:49,760 --> 01:02:53,560
David Lilly,
I want to be your agent.

1008
01:02:53,640 --> 01:02:55,160
I can make the deals
with the studios

1009
01:02:55,240 --> 01:02:56,640
that you need to have made.

1010
01:02:56,720 --> 01:02:59,360
I will have the studio people
over here catering to you.

1011
01:02:59,440 --> 01:03:01,320
I will have them
doing your yard work.

1012
01:03:01,400 --> 01:03:04,080
I will have them
cleaning out your litter box.

1013
01:03:04,160 --> 01:03:05,480
I want to make you
so much money

1014
01:03:05,560 --> 01:03:08,760
