repping me, too.

1020
01:03:25,920 --> 01:03:27,160
Okay, fine.

1021
01:03:27,240 --> 01:03:28,320
You're my agent.
You're my agent.

1022
01:03:28,400 --> 01:03:30,920
Just get off my lawn
before the cops come.

1023
01:03:32,600 --> 01:03:33,560
Yes!

1024
01:03:33,640 --> 01:03:36,880
You're not gonna regret this.
Thank you. Thank you!

1025
01:03:36,920 --> 01:03:40,240
I'm very excited.
Very excited!

